{"tid":1660913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勇武獅子章】呢 個 章 可 能 幫 到 勇 武","createTime":"2019-10-17T21:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T23:41:08.000Z","uid":154486,"like":17,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2abdc59cb3f64e1256fe091804cadeee7a2c6d87","tid":1660913,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:06:35.000Z","msg":"我地有一班人，好鐘意之前「永不割席」巴打既一張獅子徽號：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2amBf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2amBf2.jpg&h=7fdf2f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然好多人對於所謂香港未來「國徽」仲未有定論，但係我地覺得呢個徽號本身係好適合勇武<br />\n所以我地自己係佢既靚靚設計上面再大加修改：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPyDDUo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPyDDUo.jpg&h=cc0966bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能你會問，又話比人睇既，點解咁低清，又有水印呢？<br />\n<br />\n原因好簡單：<strong>呢個章只會出現係抗爭現場</strong><br />\n我地揾左外國廠用呢幅圖去印一Ｄ戰術章，然後會逐少逐少送比前線<br />\n由前線既手足分比一Ｄ自己信任既人<br />\n呢個章既原圖<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只會由我地保管</span></strong><br />\n確保冇臥底可以攞到原圖大規模老翻<br />\n<br />\n當然，未來<strong><ins>有呢個章既人唔代表佢唔係鬼</ins>，<ins>冇章亦都唔代表佢係鬼</ins></strong><br />\nＤ狗咬人果陣可以搶走勇武既章比自己Ｄ臥底狗用，另外我地都唔係識曬咁多個勇武手足<br />\n呢個章，唔係乜野信物，唔係乜野地下組織標記，唔係暗號<br />\n你當係我地對勇武手足既肯定，係你地應得既勳章<br />\n<br />\n未來有機會攞到呢個章既人，平時<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>絕對不可以露眼（唔好咁ON9，係人都知你發過夢仲好勇武）</strong></span>，行動時可以考慮佩戴，必要時請隨便丟棄<br />\n你唔會知我地幾時會派，會派幾多，會比邊個<br />\n但係最理想既情況下，我地覺得，由你最信任既戰友親手交比你先係最好既做法<br />\n<br />\n因應流通程度，萬一真係比Ｄ臥底狗Copy曬／搶曬，我地絕對會再重新出一批新既，以作辨別<br />\n記住，就算對方有章，都唔等於你可以完全放心！<br />\n<br />\n如果有手足都想做類似既野，我地無任歡迎，越多野比Ｄ臥底狗煩就越好！！<br />\n希望呢個章仔可以幫到手足，最緊要係鼓舞士氣，繼續奮戰落去！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"232f0a065227fa8f29bde5b1e4ad87fffff605dc","tid":1660913,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:11:20.000Z","msg":"幾型"},{"pid":"a9776b40e0fb4e17c3439ec395d07330adb4d8d4","tid":1660913,"uid":38804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:15:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b03960b275b28c647a2b23b7e8e19aaffc14f9f","tid":1660913,"uid":2110,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:15:24.000Z","msg":"唔建議<br />\n<br />\n1. 你都講左有個章都唔代表到唔係狗，但其他人見到個章好自然減低警覺，咁好危險<br />\n<br />\n2. 面對緊國家機械，做唔到一樣，做個相似無難度，普通人無法分<br />\n<br />\n夜，要訓唔講咁多。"},{"pid":"1b3534a12914ac080ebab07b466b283b2c507006","tid":1660913,"uid":8500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:17:29.000Z","msg":"你自已都話有又唔代表唔係鬼<br />\n冇又唔代表係鬼<br />\n咁有咩用？士兵d臂章呀？"},{"pid":"5541060c32d1722b898ee38a09b13eb912125600","tid":1660913,"uid":5523,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5b03960b275b28c647a2b23b7e8e19aaffc14f9f","tid":1660913,"uid":2110,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:15:24.000Z","msg":"唔建議<br />\n<br />\n1. 你都講左有個章都唔代表到唔係狗，但其他人見到個章好自然減低警覺，咁好危險<br />\n<br />\n2. 面對緊國家機械，做唔到一樣，做個相似無難度，普通人無法分<br />\n<br />\n夜，要訓唔講咁多。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:20:36.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n為理念而戰既戰士真係需要圖騰去彰顯榮耀？<br />\n佢地要既係光復香港<br />\n要既係煲底之約"},{"pid":"a76780506e304bd14cf40462cc79246b25c69341","tid":1660913,"uid":57767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:20:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有手足都想做類似既野，我地無任歡迎，越多野比Ｄ臥底狗煩就越好！！<br />\n希望呢個章仔可以幫到手足，最緊要係鼓舞士氣，繼續奮戰落去！</span><br />\n<br />\n重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581cbf962d3fc91ef7c7475272ef133798258346","tid":1660913,"uid":1187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:24:16.000Z","msg":"完全睇唔到有咩用途...."},{"pid":"b0d1ef0fac75fabcb3f0658e452738e26c7359d9","tid":1660913,"uid":2110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a76780506e304bd14cf40462cc79246b25c69341","tid":1660913,"uid":57767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:20:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有手足都想做類似既野，我地無任歡迎，越多野比Ｄ臥底狗煩就越好！！<br />\n希望呢個章仔可以幫到手足，最緊要係鼓舞士氣，繼續奮戰落去！</span><br />\n<br />\n重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:25:41.000Z","msg":"其實比人搜到有依個章，即係直接同狗講，可以落重資源查依個人<br />\n<br />\n根本無乜好處"},{"pid":"1b044fb0ee710a4cc28aa25b94e08ae05abaa21b","tid":1660913,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:25:58.000Z","msg":"頭兩個Comment已經代表呢個Post玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過正如我地所講，過幾個月呢Ｄ章逐少逐少就會出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757d24e88b5ca9cc5cc9780f426cc469e17b10f0","tid":1660913,"uid":9759,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:27:15.000Z","msg":"你戴住個章出去 咪即係擺明車馬話比人知你係勇武<br />\n行到出去black bloc 既意義去左邊<br />\n比班黑警見到就即刻拉哂先 而差佬查cctv個時又方便左<br />\n完全唔覺呢個章有咩可以幫到勇武<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c20f641b04adbefe0db03888db3f891de6be34","tid":1660913,"uid":162221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:29:18.000Z","msg":"有章等陣d鬼見到第一個衝埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353d157aca9467a4daed0414f1afb7d714c50e31","tid":1660913,"uid":8500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3c20f641b04adbefe0db03888db3f891de6be34","tid":1660913,"uid":162221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:29:18.000Z","msg":"有章等陣d鬼見到第一個衝埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:30:46.000Z","msg":"爽呀唔洗驚捉錯和理非<br />\n搜證入罪都易d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0027de6661c81738de96ed1f95710b27ffb8b9","tid":1660913,"uid":76674,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:33:20.000Z","msg":"有章=拉得？<br />\n同預約拘捕有咩分別？<br />\n越少記認越好，拉咗都易打甩<br />\n無啦啦搞啲咁既野只會搞散前線<br />\n分化有章冇章勇武"},{"pid":"86d64e9c6878f1c5595cd890996394bb7e807399","tid":1660913,"uid":4156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:33:43.000Z","msg":"想做大台 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e366c6fe3b951cd6e1203878bf9cdacc4a80b4","tid":1660913,"uid":68220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:34:10.000Z","msg":"專捉有章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話畀人懷疑係狗個陣拎出黎都合理啲<br />\n但又冇原版<br />\n對條撚呀"},{"pid":"2aabc0d64751546f70e06e499cdcec041a840c38","tid":1660913,"uid":4156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"353d157aca9467a4daed0414f1afb7d714c50e31","tid":1660913,"uid":8500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3c20f641b04adbefe0db03888db3f891de6be34","tid":1660913,"uid":162221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:29:18.000Z","msg":"有章等陣d鬼見到第一個衝埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:30:46.000Z","msg":"爽呀唔洗驚捉錯和理非<br />\n搜證入罪都易d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:41:13.000Z","msg":"笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話比人知自己係勇武 咁black bloc 黎托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d082637e3f027a3b759b66203930119d7ace092c","tid":1660913,"uid":28042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:48:44.000Z","msg":"好撚蠢，咁blackbloc 仲有咩用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e8a7d4f64498e17c4442d723f7b23cc1a7df9a","tid":1660913,"uid":76674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:48:54.000Z","msg":"拿，我建議樓主抄running man咁，大大隻字寫住&quot;勇武&quot;整個名牌痴係背脊，有背囊就痴心口，撕開有埋全名，身份證號碼，屋企地址咁，方便黑警做野吖嘛，半夜三更開啲咁既post，都唔知係未訓醒定係眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508ecda8d4aa79c4775c5454eee1edd698477ffd","tid":1660913,"uid":17263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:48:56.000Z","msg":"唔好<br />\nBlack bloc 就係要一式一樣<br />\n有啲咁嘅嘢咪同漆黑中嘅螢火蟲一樣 咁鮮明 咁出眾"},{"pid":"4ae2e7ed354e57409a7e450724aded252ee262fb","tid":1660913,"uid":34065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:49:29.000Z","msg":"咪搞埋d多餘野啦 諗下戰術 裝備 逃生路線 方法<br />\n好過做埋d 形式野啦 <br />\n真係好似樓上講 係前線帶哂 等等狗專咬依d抗爭者<br />\n或者捉幾個有依d章既抗爭者  然後由臥底帶上<br />\n再借個章去令勇武抗爭者放下戒心 再捉人<br />\n真係多謝你個飛機章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩真係勇武 上前線絕對唔好帶<br />\nblackbloc 愈少記認就愈好 幫到自己又幫到人<br />\n(勇武小隊自己特別記認 就例外)"},{"pid":"fde9c661bacdd285f8dd722c7706ef553857424c","tid":1660913,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:51:04.000Z","msg":"膠POST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359061f43b3d3989e4ce3db5f2b1ef8a19e94470","tid":1660913,"uid":40750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:51:10.000Z","msg":"有既唔一定係<br />\n無既唔一定唔係<br />\n派個無用既記認出去Fake自己友咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議可以小隊化整唔同章+Keep著換章加大調查成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79dd5ea925f9e2e6076ad7d95fa6cf91035d2015","tid":1660913,"uid":114707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:53:14.000Z","msg":"但咁咪無咗blackbloc精髓"},{"pid":"b9de353704d7b655f947f625e129b8ecd0901e27","tid":1660913,"uid":56627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T21:58:45.000Z","msg":"樓主=鬼"}]}